author: eTN Editor
title: Thai bus crash sends tourists to hospital
text:
Thai bus crash sends tourists to hospital Adv: 
Jul 27, 2015 Adv: 
At around 12:00 noon local time today, Sunday, July 26, 2015, on Bypass road in Phuket, Thailand, a bus flipped over, injuring 17 tourists from China. All the injured were sent to a nearby hospital, one was seriously injured. 
No deaths were reported. 
Police are investigating the cause of the accident.
